				<title>11. 支持多字母的局部变量</title>
				<link>https://rendcrx.github.io/posts/compiler/chibicc/11.-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F/</link>
